# React Import Rule

Never use a default React import. Always use named imports only.

## Correct

```js
import { useState, useEffect, useRef } from "react";
import { memo, forwardRef, useCallback } from "react";
```

## Wrong

```js
// Do NOT do any of these:
import React from "react";
import React, { useState } from "react";
import * as React from "react";
```

JSX transformation does not require a React default import. Only import the specific hooks, utilities, or types you actually use.
